.DT
whisper
$MUDNAME$ player help
whisper

.SH Name
.SI 5
whisper - Whisper to another person.
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
whisper <message> to <person>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This is similar to tell, except it only works in the current room and it
tells everyone else in the room that you whispered to the person, but not
what.  This command is great for inducing paranoia.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> whisper you are not a frog to shiannar
You whisper to shiannar: you are not a frog.
.EI
Messages everyone else gets
.SI 5
Windy whispers something to Shiannar.
.EI
Message Shiannar gets.
.SI 5
Windy whispers to you: you are not a frog.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
say, ssay, lsay, shout, tell, emote, sayto
.EI
